expression = re.compile(rfc._RFC1123_DATETIME_REGEX)
good_examples = ['Mon, 31 Oct 1982 03:21:45 GMT',
    'Thu, 01 Feb 2045 20:34:22 GMT']
for good_example in good_examples:
    self.assertTrue(bool(expression.fullmatch(good_example)), msg=
        "Good rfc1123 datetime '{d}' didn't match regex".format(d=good_example)
        )
